title: Ep. 186 "I Have To Tell You Something...I Have Herpes" ft. Jenelle @thestiproject
description:
This week we have Jenelle Pierce, Executive Director of the STI Project to share her journey with herpes and information to help others be more informed about Herpes and other STI's.

If you'd like to reach out to Jenelle feel free to connect with her on all social platforms @thestiproject or visit her at www.thestiproject.com

We've got more bonus content! Join us at www.patreon.com/cocktales
